The @GrindingMocks consensus board doesn't list a single RB in the first round of the upcoming #NFLDraft2022. Did teams significantly reduce 1st round pick investments in running backs?

I investigated @pfref data and the answer is: Yes.
#nflverse #rstats https://t.co/ntjjNA0JY5

How does Matt Araiza's 2021 Ray Guy Award winning season stack up against the NFL's best punters from last season using SYLOE?

Pretty well as it turns out.

#nflverse https://t.co/D2cB22iKtc
